OL,3,CTwo men charged after human remains
OL,4,Cfound in woodland
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter the discovery of human remains
OL,8,Fin Salford.
OL,10,FEarlier discoveries were made at
OL,11,FKersal Dale, Blackleach Reservoir and
OL,12,FColliery Wood, all in Salford, over
OL,13,Fthe past three weeks. The first
OL,14,Fdiscovery was on 4 April.
OL,16,Fbelieve the victim was a man in his
OL,17,F60s from Salford.
