OL,3,CTwo men charged after human remains
OL,4,Cfound in woodland
OL,6,FMichal Jaroslaw Polchowski, 70, and
OL,7,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, both of
OL,8,FWorsley Road, Eccles, have been
OL,9,Fcharged with murder.
OL,11,FThey are due to appear at Tameside
OL,12,FMagistrates Court on Monday 29 April.
OL,14,FFormal identification is ongoing. The
OL,15,Fremains that were found at the other
OL,16,Fthree locations are still being tested.
OL,18,FPolice say they are 'confident' they
OL,19,Fbelong to the same victim.
