OL,4,Cfound in woodland
OL,6,FACC Sarah Jackson said, "We have had
OL,7,Flarge numbers of officers, staff and
OL,8,Fspecialists working diligently on this
OL,9,Finvestigation over the last three
OL,10,Fweeks. It has been very much a large,
OL,11,Fcollective effort, with the victim and
OL,12,Ffamily at the heart of it from the
OL,13,Foutset.
OL,15,F"We have specially trained officers
OL,16,Fdeployed to support the family as they
OL,17,Fcome to terms with this tragic news.
OL,18,FThey are aware of this morning's
OL,19,Ffurther discovery and will continue to
OL,20,Fbe kept up to date with how we are
OL,21,Fprogressing.
