OL,6,F"Despite the charges brought today,
OL,7,Four work is far from over.
OL,9,F"The scenes we already have
OL,10,Festablished in Bury and Salford will
OL,11,Fremain in place for much of this week
OL,12,Fwhilst our searches and enquiries
OL,13,Fcontinue. Local officers will continue
OL,14,Fto patrol the impacted areas to
OL,15,Fprovide reassurance.
OL,17,F"We will continue following every line
OL,18,Fof enquiry to recover and reunite the
OL,19,Fvictim with his family, bringing a
OL,20,Fdignified end to this terrible
OL,21,Fscenario.
