OL,6,F"I'd like to thank the communities of
OL,7,FSalford and beyond for their
OL,8,Fcooperation throughout this
OL,9,Finvestigation. I know this incident
OL,10,Fhas come as a shock, and the support
OL,11,Fwe've had from those in the area is
OL,12,Fvery much appreciated."
